reviewText: The son-in law was very pleased.
Very cute! My mom loved it and the DVD was very interesting!
This was really cheesy. Next time I'll definitely lower my expectations.
Love this as a novelty gift!

I'll bet that you did not know about Eisenhower attending a dedication at the Washington, D.C., ISLAMIC CENTER, and calling it beautiful.  But you probably DO remember, if you are an old fart like me, that advertisements on TV were crazy and stupid and sometimes beautiful (when they had ballet dancing around refrigerators, for example).  OMG, I always thought 1957 was The Last Good Year, and maybe it was.
This was a gift. It was delivered on time and the recipient said the video was funny & informative for the year he was born! He really enjoyed this gift.
What memories! Very enjoyable! A fun trip down memory lane. Recommend!
